StringValues.15: A large commemorative statue  of a Gromnie crafted by the Arcanum Tinker, in reward for destroying the statues threatening the cities of Samsur and Al-Arqas.
StringValues.7: This trophy is given to you in recognition of your valor and loyalty to the throne of New Aluvia. The Arcanum and the townsfolk of Samsur and Al-Arqas will forever be in your debt.
